name: "Discipline" Men's Black Shirt V Neck
description:
"Discipline" refers to the training that one gives one's self to accomplish a certain task or to adopt a particular pattern of behavior, even though one would really rather be doing something else. For example, denying oneself of an extravagant pleasure in order to accomplish a more demanding goal. Thus, self-discipline is the assertion of willpower over more base desires.
